---
title: Texan Black Bean Salad with Pepper Jack Frico, Pickled Red Onion & Cilantro-Lime Ranch Dressing
description: Everything’s bigger in Texas and this salad is no exception. Our chefs pulled out all the colors and deliciousness for this hearty dinner! Red shines through with tomato and pickled red onion, you’ll get some yellow with crumbled pepper Jack frico on top. Green comes in with fresh, crisp romaine lettuce, and a dressing that includes cilantro and lime zest. Tex Mex-spiced black beans add a pop of protein and flavor. Pull up ‘yer boot straps... and a chair!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/texan-black-bean-salad-f46589b2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/texan-black-bean-salad-61795c35156f11647261f16a-7378be60.pdf
author: HelloFresh
time required: 30 minutes
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/texan-black-bean-salad-61795c35156f11647261f16a
course: main course
cuisine: Mexican
